text: Victor Franklin Banks (born 8 November 1947)Victor Banks Caribbean Elections is an Anguillan politician. He was a member of the Anguilla United Front (AUF). He was Premier from 14 May 2019Anguilla's new government sworn into office Anguilla News, 24 April 2015 until he lost his re-election bid in the 2020 general election. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Chief Ministers of Anguilla Category:Premiers of Anguilla Category:Living people
